# Project Architecture and Stack Information

## Critical Rules

### Project Overview
- Project uses Laravel 12 as backend framework
- React is used as frontend framework
- Inertia.js connects Laravel with React
- Project follows modern full-stack development practices

### Backend (Laravel) Architecture
- Authentication system with social login support (Google, Facebook, GitHub, GitLab)
- Profile management with email verification
- Database uses migrations and transactions
- Testing with PHPUnit and DatabaseTransactions
- MVC architecture with Controllers, Models, and Views
- Secure password hashing and token management
- Type hinting and strict types in PHP

