#### File Naming Conventions
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `Button.jsx`, `UserProfile.jsx`)
- Hooks: camelCase, prefix with 'use' (e.g., `useAuth.js`, `useForm.js`)
- Utils: camelCase (e.g., `format.js`, `validation.js`)
- Pages: PascalCase, match route name (e.g., `Index.jsx`, `Show.jsx`)
- Types: PascalCase, suffix with type (e.g., `UserType.ts`, `SprintInterface.ts`)

